---
By: Gautama Buddha
Locus:
  Page: 40
  Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Cause
---
Not in the heavens above, nor in the farthest reaches of the sea, nor by
transporting yourself to the remotest valleys of the mountains, will you be
able to hide from the consequences of your own evil actions. Likewise,
certain are the blessings growing out of your good actions.
